<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>调用链 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E9%93%BE/</link><description>调用链 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E9%93%BE/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>CAT分布式监控</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7/cat%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7/cat%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="cat分布式监控">CAT分布式监控</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：CAT通过客户端埋点采集监控数据，通过消息树组织调用链，通过服务端聚合分析，实现从应用性能到业务指标的全链路监控，埋点规范和数据采样是落地关键。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="cat通过客户端埋点采集消息树组织服务端聚合实现全链路监控和实时告警">CAT通过客户端埋点采集、消息树组织、服务端聚合，实现全链路监控和实时告警</h2>
<h3 id="核心概念transactioneventheartbeatmetric">核心概念：Transaction、Event、Heartbeat、Metric</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>类型</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>示例</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Transaction</td>
          <td>有执行时间的嵌套结构</td>
          <td>SQL执行、RPC调用、方法执行</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Event</td>
          <td>无执行时间的离散事件</td>
          <td>异常、日志、用户行为</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Heartbeat</td>
          <td>周期性心跳</td>
          <td>JVM状态、线程数、系统负载</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Metric</td>
          <td>指标统计</td>
          <td>QPS、RT、成功率</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">消息树（Message Tree）结构：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Root Transaction: URL-/api/order/create
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── Transaction: Service-createOrder (耗时50ms)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── Transaction: DAO-insertOrder (耗时10ms)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   │   └── Event: SQL (INSERT INTO order ...)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   ├── Transaction: Cache-getUser (耗时5ms)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── Transaction: RPC-callPayment (耗时30ms)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│       └── Event: Request (payId=12345)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── Event: OrderCreated (orderId=10001)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── Metric: order.create (count=1)</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
